{"tid":865622,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【又有壞消息】傳騰訊再多兩款棋牌類網遊下架","createTime":"2018-10-17T08:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T12:02:21.000Z","uid":100155,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"926b2b4e4c1a1945b3e7ffec531225c153c1511f","tid":865622,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"內地棋牌類網絡遊戲或迎來寒冬，繼騰訊(00700)旗下遊戲《天天德州》宣布退市後，內地傳媒報道，另外兩款遊戲《歡樂拼三張》和《歡樂鬥棋牌》亦確認將退市。騰訊稱，關閉相關遊戲的原因是「公司業務策略調整」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，另一家網遊公司博雅互動(00434)曾經在中期業績中透露，「市場傳聞中國政府將出台《棋牌類網絡遊戲管理辦法》，下架德州撲克類遊戲及從2018年6月1日起，全面禁止運營德州撲克遊戲」。博雅指出，雖然政策尚未出台，但部分平台已對相關產品進行下架處理。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，內地監管機構近期連番打擊網上遊戲，有傳內地凍結遊戲審批，同時又擬向每款網絡遊戲徵收35%的專項稅。此外，內地早前公布《綜合防控兒童青少年近視實施方案》通知當中，提到將實施網絡遊戲總量調控，控制新增網絡遊戲網運營數量。<br />\n<br />\n責編：郭韻婷"},{"pid":"2b8ff78fb7ee262726087546fbe086fef1c750d0","tid":865622,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"就算call/牛都唔好太high呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1707dce61e2b685fdfb960b26edd424ccd73d646","tid":865622,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"old new so ex西停<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc//stocks/quote_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280911343&amp;code=777&amp;section=related&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2F%2Fstocks%2Fquote_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN280911343%26code%3D777%26section%3Drelated%26page%3D1&d=Z1qCflbjvdOU9%2BWWpJONNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=864d08a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc//stocks/quote_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280911343&amp;code=777&amp;section=related&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n11/09/2018 14:57"},{"pid":"d32381e443d17ac131022adfcd2f37ba600484de","tid":865622,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"佢一彈，又再熊佢<br />\n起碼落$180先好講野"},{"pid":"3ae58e261a1307e8b5384226da71e58e75bb5e4c","tid":865622,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"同呢啲支那閪股過人世咩<br />\n支那對住侵侵死狗咁<br />\n但對住騰訊就劍劍封喉<br />\n咪放長雙眼睇隻閪船有幾多斤釘囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b1c7d0cf81b2c9254d324e1176fb76e5497f4c","tid":865622,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"牛三照升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ed80f15bfe70af25aa291bfd3e197246ee0551","tid":865622,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d32381e443d17ac131022adfcd2f37ba600484de","tid":865622,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"佢一彈，又再熊佢<br />\n起碼落$180先好講野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"啱"}]}